    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 90,
    "rowsha": "t+DHPxrMsHxWSDHcVfOi3WwbAYJqtWokQyDIIIAY7/g=",
    "originContent": "Alternatively, you can run the development server directly: `yarn dev` or `yarn dev:nocache`",
    "translatedContent": "または、開発サーバーを直接実行できます：`yarn dev` または `yarn dev:nocache`"
  },
  {
    "row": 91,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 92,
    "rowsha": "Xvd03TqEc8dCArJs8T0LE0Biltq1/Dz3n9um5HHe3h4=",
    "originContent": "If you wish to use a base path for the application other than root (`/`), you must build it manually while setting `URL_BASE_PATH` to your preferred base path.",
    "translatedContent": "アプリケーションのベースパスをルート（`/`）以外にしたい場合は、`URL_BASE_PATH`を希望のベースパスに設定して手動でビルドする必要があります。"
  },
  {
    "row": 93,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 94,
    "rowsha": "lJ+/CuHLBHy3NHO+/TigQayygGZ/7hg1w+ou/d8JFTM=",
    "originContent": "Leave the configuration as the default, or change [`config.json`](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Stannnnn/jelly-app/main/public/config.json) as needed. Configurations are explained on the [App Configuration Section](#app-configuration).",
    "translatedContent": "設定はデフォルトのままにするか、必要に応じて[`config.json`](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Stannnnn/jelly-app/main/public/config.json)を変更してください。設定については[アプリ設定セクション](#app-configuration)で説明しています。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 95,
    "rowsha": "vZ179DRN73jrn/hlYwk2hZ2TLfPCJWLso6/nQMPX3bc=",
    "originContent": "The `config.json` file can be changed directly in the built application afterwards. There is no need to rebuild if only changing a configuration variable.",
    "translatedContent": "ビルド後でも`config.json`ファイルは直接変更可能です。設定変数のみの変更であれば再ビルドは不要です。"
  },
  {
    "row": 96,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
