  },
  {
    "row": 163,
    "rowsha": "O8kelGUp/h+c+Tfp5LMiH7Ber4TzExp1JPi66T1VzGE=",
    "originContent": "For easier container management, you can use Docker Compose. A `docker-compose.yaml` file is provided in the repository with sensible defaults.",
    "translatedContent": "コンテナ管理を容易にするために、Docker Composeを使用できます。リポジトリには適切なデフォルト設定がされた`docker-compose.yaml`ファイルが用意されています。"
  },
  {
    "row": 164,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 165,
    "rowsha": "09oKqPu+KsMG7l8dngRQYD+IDcwCCOTZKdg+o/3SflI=",
    "originContent": "1.  Copy the example environment file and customize it for your setup:",
    "translatedContent": "1.  環境設定の例ファイルをコピーし、セットアップに合わせてカスタマイズしてください："
  },
  {
    "row": 166,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 167,
    "rowsha": "S7nEzVArg6C6TspYFuMUz99BG48kmz2TfKb0lMAEDq0=",
    "originContent": "    ```bash",
    "translatedContent": "    ```bash"
  },
  {
    "row": 168,
    "rowsha": "5zruuHYAfIogrPcUgtiURyohEX28sDhgg6G/r0W/ZPc=",
    "originContent": "    cp .env.example .env",
    "translatedContent": "    cp .env.example .env"
  },
  {
    "row": 169,
    "rowsha": "7em5kHTNO1cPWnaxB4H1GFdKMaKdWtteFc09etZSl0o=",
    "originContent": "    ```",
    "translatedContent": "    ```"
  },
  {
    "row": 170,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 171,
    "rowsha": "IzvzQtt+SUNe4RODYduk2Fih8WOV22d5u590uVh7LpQ=",
    "originContent": "2.  Edit the `.env` file with your Jellyfin server URL and preferences:",
    "translatedContent": "2.  `.env` ファイルを編集して、Jellyfin サーバーのURLと設定を入力します:"
  },
  {
    "row": 172,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 173,
    "rowsha": "QKePe3J0XsrTA4idIeRUiXBop6e9rX5lpD0+LZsc5R0=",
    "originContent": "    ```env",
    "translatedContent": "    ```env"
  },
  {
    "row": 174,
    "rowsha": "q7Sd2YLJBF5lbOB4ZOEJn/6yI2L/l2s6seubOxBUWWA=",
    "originContent": "    JELLYAPP_PORT=80",
    "translatedContent": "    JELLYAPP_PORT=80"
  },
  {
    "row": 175,
    "rowsha": "58EYSAnNDhJjp7jz0EtsPOaixZliAs0mJfvvpPI6rqY=",
    "originContent": "    JELLYAPP_DEFAULT_URL=https://demo.jellyfin.org/stable",
    "translatedContent": "    JELLYAPP_DEFAULT_URL=https://demo.jellyfin.org/stable"
  },
  {
    "row": 176,
    "rowsha": "zhGpRgIXuQQ+/H74gUZqpND7AiB3rjHJYTyMlwnevu4=",
    "originContent": "    JELLYAPP_LOCK_URL=true",
    "translatedContent": "    JELLYAPP_LOCK_URL=true"
  },
  {
    "row": 177,
    "rowsha": "7em5kHTNO1cPWnaxB4H1GFdKMaKdWtteFc09etZSl0o=",
    "originContent": "    ```",
    "translatedContent": "    ```"
  },
  {
    "row": 178,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 179,
    "rowsha": "y4VGx22ndpJ7B66p4GcXtYgWwMUpZro7mXLkzZAzYrg=",
    "originContent": "3.  Start the container using Docker Compose:",
    "translatedContent": "3.  Docker Composeを使用してコンテナを起動します:"
  },
  {
    "row": 180,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
