    "row": 181,
    "rowsha": "S7nEzVArg6C6TspYFuMUz99BG48kmz2TfKb0lMAEDq0=",
    "originContent": "    ```bash",
    "translatedContent": "    ```bash"
  },
  {
    "row": 182,
    "rowsha": "GTHDXBuvKW4Hmm0wzDKKcAoiYtSYo9XUsaoXCSZI858=",
    "originContent": "    docker-compose up -d",
    "translatedContent": "    docker-compose up -d"
  },
  {
    "row": 183,
    "rowsha": "7em5kHTNO1cPWnaxB4H1GFdKMaKdWtteFc09etZSl0o=",
    "originContent": "    ```",
    "translatedContent": "    ```"
  },
  {
    "row": 184,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 185,
    "rowsha": "1fskpI2CpAvXhpBwZGFzRzPwt8vIZ/8GQtqQXwMLK2Q=",
    "originContent": "The `docker-compose.yaml` file uses environment variables with the following defaults:",
    "translatedContent": "`docker-compose.yaml` ファイルは、以下のデフォルト値を持つ環境変数を使用しています:"
  },
  {
    "row": 186,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 187,
    "rowsha": "cVWA0Su9k37iZ8zCqYHDzY/TMyOLL8umQoF0eLq4R18=",
    "originContent": "- `JELLYAPP_PORT`: External port to expose (default: `80`)",
    "translatedContent": "- `JELLYAPP_PORT`: 公開する外部ポート（デフォルト: `80`）"
  },
  {
    "row": 188,
    "rowsha": "bTPKRMyEWpLs4/mEEBRUEBeESF9y9xenB1Y7AqMtamw=",
    "originContent": "- `JELLYAPP_DEFAULT_URL`: Default Jellyfin server URL (default: `https://demo.jellyfin.org/stable`)",
    "translatedContent": "- `JELLYAPP_DEFAULT_URL`: デフォルトのJellyfinサーバーURL（デフォルト: `https://demo.jellyfin.org/stable`）"
  },
  {
    "row": 189,
    "rowsha": "k+u3rYa7Ad15jCRH5yA9YRVl7durngUK8eXLT0yYK3E=",
    "originContent": "- `JELLYAPP_LOCK_URL`: Lock the Jellyfin URL input (default: `false`)",
    "translatedContent": "- `JELLYAPP_LOCK_URL`: JellyfinのURL入力をロック（デフォルト: `false`）"
  },
  {
    "row": 190,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 191,
    "rowsha": "OBYS14+pj7TwNRhIMfGA66+CnGT4Nf2uUsz6rV+EMI4=",
    "originContent": "### App Configuration",
    "translatedContent": "### アプリ設定"
  },
  {
    "row": 192,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 193,
    "rowsha": "6MwfkGRuK3k0QS2Y9WvToosAuZeDKM8o/CGQ4/VmCWQ=",
    "originContent": "App configuration can be modified by editing the `config.json` file during the build process or in the release files. When using Docker, configurations can be provided as environment variables. The available configuration options are as follows:",
    "translatedContent": "アプリの設定は、ビルドプロセス中またはリリースファイル内の `config.json` ファイルを編集して変更できます。Dockerを使用する場合は、環境変数として設定を提供できます。利用可能な設定オプションは以下の通りです:"
  },
  {
    "row": 194,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 195,
    "rowsha": "9aU3/304HmfOf5EC93O8pdQccX1c6lFvAoZMgeW6ePo=",
    "originContent": "- `DEFAULT_JELLYFIN_URL`: Sets the default Jellyfin server URL loaded on first app access if no URL is stored in Local Storage.",
    "translatedContent": "- `DEFAULT_JELLYFIN_URL`: ローカルストレージにURLが保存されていない場合、アプリ初回アクセス時に読み込まれるデフォルトのJellyfinサーバーURLを設定します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 196,
    "rowsha": "m+D8zrfIhk7uTh+xlTAkWpUc+xeJDXhGOBg+5lz2mJM=",
    "originContent": "- `LOCK_JELLYFIN_URL`: If set to `true`, removes the URL input field and enforces the default URL (`DEFAULT_JELLYFIN_URL`) for all connections, ideal for self-hosted instances tied to a single server.",
    "translatedContent": "- `LOCK_JELLYFIN_URL`: `true` に設定すると、URL入力欄が削除され、すべての接続に対してデフォルトURL（`DEFAULT_JELLYFIN_URL`）が強制されます。これは単一サーバーに紐づいたセルフホスト環境に最適です。"
  },
  {
    "row": 197,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 198,
    "rowsha": "5ww9yAUhltb679bzey3v6rRmdriJbfvnrASADmXR90c=",
